# The classic trend regime, on the sector that trends hardest: enter the
# golden cross, exit the death cross. The [after] backstop caps dead money
# if the averages go sideways for a year — a cross that never resolves is
# its own signal.

strategy "Semis Trend Rider"

universe [semis]
timeframe 1d

when [sma 50] crosses above [sma 200]
  buy [10% portfolio]

sell when [sma 50] crosses below [sma 200]
  or [after 250 bars]

risk [max_positions 4] [max_position 15%]
